description:
OmniPage Cloud Service (OCS) is a SaaS solution that provides document processing services. The goals of OCS are to
      •	enable no-setup usage of Nuance’s Capture SDK.
      •	provide a ready-to-use, solid and scaling document conversion platform for ISVs.
      •	enable the development of OCR-intensive applications for devices short on computational power.
      OCS is a cloud service aiming at improved scalability and reliability.

      Register at https://portal.nuancecomputing.com for OCS access key and full SDK.
releaseNotes:
First release nuget packaging of the .NET rest client to access OCS functionality in the cloud.
      Current OCS release notes can be reviewed at https://portal.nuancecomputing.com/RN/03172014
summary: Omnipage Cloud Service (OCS) is a cloud hosted web service offering digital document processing capabilities and OCR.
